{"tid":2356961,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[白左當道]Twitch 因當事人言論移除 PogChamp 表情","createTime":"2021-01-07T06:15:59.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-07T06:15:59.000Z","uid":392,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b1e9d7cdc09842f599326eba97f2e3abb0cef965","tid":2356961,"uid":392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T06:15:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/C_Chat/M.1609988213.A.2CB.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ptt.cc%2Fbbs%2FC_Chat%2FM.1609988213.A.2CB.html&d=tgCcTb3Ji4LFIEkqsM1g5rTKTGNgLIIXgyzGYx6bzTs%3D&h=3619b758\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/C_Chat/M.1609988213.A.2CB.html</a><br />\n<br />\nTwitch 表示該表情意義重大，已經遠超當事人或圖片本身<br />\n是 Twitch 文化重要的一部份，但是繼續允許這個表情存在有違他們的良心<br />\n未來會想辦法研發出適合類似情境使用的替代表情<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n表情當事人的推特<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/gootecks/status/1346945376318746626\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fgootecks%2Fstatus%2F1346945376318746626&d=tgCcTb3Ji4LFIEkqsM1g5rTKTGNgLIIXgyzGYx6bzTs%3D&h=38f689f1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fgootecks%2Fstatus%2F1346945376318746626&h=c920e941\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/gootecks/status/1346945376318746626</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">&quot;群眾會為了今天在國會暴動中被射殺的女性上街示威抗議嗎？&quot;<br />\n&quot;還是MAGA（Make America Great Again）烈士將會白白犧牲？&quot;</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nPogChamp 的原始出處是一支 2010 年的採訪影片<br />\n職業快打旋風選手兼實況主 Ryan Gutierrez（Gootecks）<br />\n看到攝影師撞到三角架導致鏡頭晃動而擺出的表情<br />\n之後在網路竄紅，並於 2012 年被 Twitch 製作為表情"}]}